#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/numpy_interface/numpy_algorithms.py:7
msgid ""
"This internal module provides a number of algorithms designed to be "
"compatible with and used by numpy. In particular, some algorithms required "
"to be adapted to handle VTKCompositeDataArray. Note that the decorated "
"functions (by _override_numpy) are not meant to be called directly from here "
"but directly through the Numpy API."
msgstr ""

