"another argument The second argument can be a VTKCompositeDataArray, in "
"which case a one-to-one match between arrays is assumed. Otherwise, the "
"function is applied to the composite array with the second argument "
"repeated. VTKArray and numpy arrays are also supported."
msgstr ""

